39
00:05:46.638 --> 00:05:49.683 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>After all, why did I, Wild Tiger,</i>

40
00:05:49.933 --> 00:05:52.561 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>have to partner with</i>
<i>some smart-ass, hotshot kid?</i>

41
00:05:54.437 --> 00:05:59.568 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
