look at me like that.

47
00:06:33.643 --> 00:06:36.229 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[choking up]
Please, man, ya gotta remember...

48
00:06:36.897 --> 00:06:38.440 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You're my partner!

49
00:06:39.065 --> 00:06:40.358 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
And we were the
best team ever--!

50
00:06:40.525 --> 00:06:41.902 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Shut up!

51
00:06:52.037 --> 00:06:55.415 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
How dare you dishonor
Wild Tiger's name!

52
00:06:57.542 --> 00:06:59.878 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
