for Samantha.

53
00:07:02.631 --> 00:07:03.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[suit]
<i>Good Luck.</i>

54
00:07:06.301 --> 00:07:08.261 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
So this is how it ends, huh?

55
00:07:09.262 --> 00:07:11.306 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Take care, Lil' Bunny.

56
00:07:19.814 --> 00:07:21.900 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
