57
00:07:25.570 --> 00:07:27.864 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
The name is Barnaby, not Bunny.

58
00:07:31.409 --> 00:07:34.955 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
