61
00:07:44.506 --> 00:07:46.591 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Huh? Well obviously.

62
00:07:46.883 --> 00:07:49.094 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
