call me "Bunny," okay?

64
00:07:52.013 --> 00:07:53.056 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hm...

65
00:07:53.640 --> 00:07:56.726 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I am not a Bunny! My name is Barnaby!

66
00:07:57.686 --> 00:08:01.272 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
