I'm glad you do.

67
00:08:01.606 --> 00:08:02.607 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
What?

68
00:08:06.444 --> 00:08:09.781 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
