You're you again!

69
00:08:10.323 --> 00:08:12.409 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Uh, what the heck are
you talking about?

70
00:08:13.368 --> 00:08:15.495 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
So, you remember me, right?

71
00:08:15.870 --> 00:08:19.207 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Were you listening to me, Old Man?
I asked you first.

72
00:08:22.252 --> 00:08:23.503 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Kotetsu?

73
00:08:24.337 --> 00:08:26.423 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[laughing]

74
00:08:26.673 --> 00:08:28.508 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hey, come on now-?!

75
