-You're hurting me!

77
00:08:33.304 --> 00:08:36.349 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Just like old times!
-What is wrong with you?

78
00:08:36.558 --> 00:08:39.728 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-It's great to have you back.
-You've really lost it, Kotetsu...

79
00:08:42.022 --> 00:08:46.818 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
