86
00:09:11.217 --> 00:09:12.218 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hm?

87
00:09:12.302 --> 00:09:15.930 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
