I betrayed you. My own partner--

88
00:09:16.056 --> 00:09:17.724 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ah don't worry about it, buddy.

89
00:09:17.891 --> 00:09:20.226 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You were under Maverick's
control the whole time.

90
00:09:22.479 --> 00:09:25.273 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
