he's been using me as a pawn.

91
00:09:26.649 --> 00:09:28.693 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
[tires screeching]

92
00:09:33.281 --> 00:09:34.491 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
Need a lift?

93
00:09:34.616 --> 00:09:35.992 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
What're you doing here Ben?

94
00:09:36.159 --> 00:09:40.080 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Hey, that's the greeting I get?
I was worried sick about you Kotetsu!

95
00:09:40.163 --> 00:09:42.290 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I rushed all the way from
home to help you out!

96
00:09:42.457 --> 00:09:43.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
How'd you know
where I was?

97
00:09:44.000 --> 00:09:47.462 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
C'mon, I drive a cab, I can
find anything in this city.

98
00:09:47.796 --> 00:09:48.838 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Who's this?

99
00:09:49.005 --> 00:09:51.549 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Oh, he was my boss
at the last company I worked for--

100
00:09:51.674 --> 00:09:54.385 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Hey, forget all that!
What's the game plan, you guys?

101
00:09:54.511 --> 00:09:55.553 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Game plan?

102
00:09:56.304 --> 00:09:58.223 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I think it’s time to get to work.

103
00:09:58.765 --> 00:10:00.391 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-You got that right.
-Yeah.

104
00:10:00.642 --> 00:10:04.062 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
