now what?!

108
00:10:09.901 --> 00:10:11.111 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Let's go guys.

109
00:10:12.570 --> 00:10:14.656 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[in unison]
Mister Saito?

110
00:10:18.159 --> 00:10:21.037 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
