quite a scuffle earlier.

111
00:10:21.579 --> 00:10:22.789 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sorry about that.

112
00:10:23.081 --> 00:10:25.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You came all this way
to give us new suits?

113
00:10:26.626 --> 00:10:30.088 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
