dangerous features it contains.

115
00:10:35.260 --> 00:10:38.054 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ah, sorry we ditched your cab, Ben.

116
00:10:38.638 --> 00:10:42.392 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Oh, don't worry about it!
This thing is way better than my ride.

117
00:10:42.684 --> 00:10:45.353 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I mean, I just drive
some dinky old taxi cab.

118
00:10:46.479 --> 00:10:48.148 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Your car does indeed suck.

119
00:10:48.231 --> 00:10:50.358 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Hey, watch your mouth,
squawk box!

120
00:10:55.238 --> 00:10:56.322 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Okay.

121
00:10:56.614 --> 00:10:58.992 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Shall I take us back to
Apollon Media?

122
00:10:59.325 --> 00:11:03.288 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Yes. But before we go,
we need to rendezvous with the others.

123
00:11:03.580 --> 00:11:04.622 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Right.

124
00:11:04.789 --> 00:11:07.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Oh! And on the way, you'll
finally get to meet my daughter.

125
00:11:07.208 --> 00:11:08.251 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sounds good.

126
00:11:08.334 --> 00:11:10.712 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I wonder if we should ask Agnes,
for her help too.

127
00:11:11.379 --> 00:11:14.215 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
