about Maverick all over TV.

128
00:11:14.424 --> 00:11:16.885 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
As soon as the world finds out,
he'll be finished.

129
00:11:16.968 --> 00:11:18.678 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-That's a great idea--!
-[Saito] Not going to happen!

130
00:11:19.429 --> 00:11:20.972 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
--Sorry.
Huh?

131
00:11:21.347 --> 00:11:24.392 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I already tried.
I went to the studio.

132
00:11:26.186 --> 00:11:27.061 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
What?

133
00:11:27.187 --> 00:11:29.522 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[unintelligible whispering]

134
00:11:30.398 --> 00:11:33.234 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Are you trying to tell me something
little man?!

135
00:11:33.484 --> 00:11:35.945 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[unintelligible whispering]

136
00:11:36.237 --> 00:11:39.115 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I have no idea what you're trying
to say to me, speak up.

137
00:11:40.617 --> 00:11:43.912 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
If you don't leave me alone,
I'm going to have to call security!

138
00:11:46.664 --> 00:11:49.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[Saito] Her memories must
have been tampered with as well.

139
00:11:49.709 --> 00:11:51.377 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Dammit.
Too bad.

140
00:11:51.544 --> 00:11:53.922 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
There are a few others we
could reach out to for help,

141
00:11:54.380 --> 00:11:57.258 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
but we can't be certain
who else Maverick may have gotten to.

142
00:11:57.467 --> 00:12:00.261 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I guess that means we're gonna have to
settle this ourselves.

143
00:12:03.598 --> 00:12:06.726 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Hey Blue Rose, guess what!
We're heading over now!

144
00:12:07.060 --> 00:12:08.853 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
